    dc:title "Fungus-feeding thrips from Australia in the worldwide genus Hoplandrothrips (Thysanoptera, Phlaeothripinae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.248739>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.248737>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.248738>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.248740> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.248739>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15 – 21. Hoplandrothrips from Australia. hemiflavus sp. n. 15 – 16: (15) head & pronotum; (16) Meso & metanotum, pelta & tergite II. hylaius sp. n. 17 – 21: (17) holotype head; (18) small male head & pronotum; (19) holotype meso & metanotum and pelta; (20) holotype pronotum; (21) male sternite V." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/248739/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.248737>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 8. Hoplandrothrips from Australia. Head & pronotum 1 – 3: (1) abrasi sp. n.; (2) bartlei sp. n.; (3) brunneicinctus sp. n. Meso & metanotum, pelta & tergite II, 4 – 8: (4) abrasi sp. n.; (5) bartlei sp. n.; (6) brunneicinctus sp. n. (7) coorongi antennal segments I – IV. (8) brunneicinctus sp. n. male mesopresternum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/248737/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.248738>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 14. Hoplandrothrips from Australia. Head & pronotum 9 – 12: (9) coorongi sp. n.; (10) fuscus; (11) gloriosi sp. n.; (12) howei sp. n. Meso & metanotum, pelta & tergite II, 13 – 14: (13) flavipes; (14) gloriosi sp. n." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/248738/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.248740>
    dc:description "FIGURES 22 – 28. Hoplandrothrips from Australia. Head & pronotum 22 – 24: (22) ibisci sp. n.; (23) oreillyi sp. n.; (24) quadriconus. Meso & metanotum, pelta & tergite II, 25 – 26: (25) ibisci sp. n.; (26) quadriconus. Mesopresternum of xanthocnemis, 27 – 28: (27) female; (28) male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/248740/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

